---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Japó 2026" description="Guia completa del viatge al Japó" section="japo">
  <div class="container" style="padding-top: 5rem; padding-bottom: 6rem;">

    <div style="margin-bottom: 4rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.25rem;">23 juliol – 14 agost 2026 · Primer viatge · En família</p>
      <h1 style="font-size: clamp(3.5rem, 10vw, 7rem); margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Japó</h1>
      <p style="font-size: 1.125rem; color: var(--color-muted); max-width: 560px; line-height: 1.7;">
        Des de Barcelona, amb escala a Abu Dhabi. Ruta circular que comença i acaba a Tokyo, cobrint les principals zones del país.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="divider"></div>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Planificació</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/ruta" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">01</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ruta</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Recorregut complet: Tokyo, Nikko, Kyoto, Nara, Osaka, Hiroshima.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/dies" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">02</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Dia a dia</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Planificació detallada per cada jornada del viatge.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/hotels" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">03</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Hotels</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Allotjament per zona i pressupost. Ryokans, hotels i recomanacions.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/transport" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">04</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Transport</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            JR Pass (val la pena?), shinkansen, Suica/IC Card, metro Tokyo, aeroports.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/pressupost" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">05</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Pressupost</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Cost diari, ATMs, efectiu vs targeta, tax-free, Wise/Revolut. Preus de referència.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Visites</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/visites" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">04</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Llocs a visitar</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Temples, barris, mercats, naturalesa. Per ciutat i per categoria.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/parcs" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">05</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Parcs d'atraccions</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            USJ (Nintendo World, Harry Potter), Tokyo DisneySea, Fuji-Q. Preus, on menjar, consells.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Compres</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/compres/electronica" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">05</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Electrònica</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Akihabara, Den Den Town. Càmeres, àudio, retro gaming. Tax-free.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/compres/akiya" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">06</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Akiya</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Cases abandonades. Portals, procediment legal, gestors i fiscalitat.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/compres/vehicles" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">07</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Vehicles JDM</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Cotxes i motos. Importació a Espanya. Empresa vs. particular.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/compres/luxe" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">08</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Béns de luxe</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Rolex, Grand Seiko, moda japonesa. Devaluació del ien i tax-free.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/ganivets" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">09</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ganivets japonesos</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Gyuto, Santoku, Yanagiba. Tojiro, Misono, Aritsugu. Acers, on comprar i si val la pena.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/ceramica" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">10</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Ceràmica i terrissa</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Arita, Bizen, Kutani, Hagi, Mashiko. Yunomi, chawan, kintsugi. Wabi-sabi i on comprar.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Esports · Material tècnic</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/esqui" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">25</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Roba d'esquí</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Descente, Phenix, Goldwin, Onyone. Esquís Ogasaka, snowboards Moss Snowstick i 011 Artistic. Col·leccions JDM, preus en euros.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/compres/tennis" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">26</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Tenis</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Yonex (VCORE Pro, EZONE, Percept), Dunlop Japan, Mizuno. Roba, sabates Asics i Yonex Power Cushion. Preus en euros.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Finances</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/finances/inversio" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">09</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Inversió</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Borsa japonesa (TSE), ETFs, immobles. Accés des d'Espanya.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/finances/fiscal" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">10</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Fiscalitat</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Comptes bancaris, Wise, IRPF, Model 720. Conveni doble imposició.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Viatge pràctic</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/sim" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">11</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">SIM i eSIM</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Comparativa Airalo, IIJmio, Holafly. Quin triar per a 20 dies amb família.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/restaurants" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">12</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Restaurants</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            On menjar per ciutat. Sushi omakase, ramen, kaiseki, menjar de carrer.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/menjar" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">18</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Plats típics</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Tot el que has de provar: sushi, ramen, wagyu, tempura, dolços. Avisos de gluten per a cada plat.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/banys" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">13</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Banys i Toto</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Onsen, sento, protocol. Com importar un Toto Washlet a Catalunya.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/te" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">14</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Te japonès</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Matcha, gyokuro, sencha, hojicha. Ippodo, Marukyu, Tsujiri. Cerimònia del te i equipament.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section style="margin-bottom: 3rem;">
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Tecnologia</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/radioaficionat" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">22</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Radioaficionat</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Yaesu, Icom, Kenwood: emissores japoneses amb preus 40–46% inferiors a Europa. FT-991A, IC-7300, IC-705. Tax-free i consideracions tècniques.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/telefonia" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">23</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Telefonia</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Sony Xperia (20–25% menys), Sharp Aquos, Fujitsu Arrows. Exclusius JDM, SIM-free, FeliCa i avisos de compatibilitat per a Espanya.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 1.5rem;">Cultura i rellotgeria</p>
      <div style="display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 1px; background: var(--color-border);">
        <a href="/japo/agenda" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">14</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Agenda cultural</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Gion Matsuri, Summer Sonic, focs artificials. Festivals juliol–agost 2026.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/rellotges" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">15</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Rellotges japonesos</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Grand Seiko, Seiko JDM, Credor, G-Shock col·leccionista. On i quin comprar.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/sumo" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">16</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Sumo</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            On veure'l, entrades, preus. Entrenaments als heya. Curiositats de l'esport nacional.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/moda" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">17</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Moda</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Yukata, calçat tradicional, Uniqlo, dissenyadors (Issey Miyake, CDG, Sacai) i artesania tèxtil.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/esqui" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">24</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Roba d'esquí</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Descente, Phenix, Goldwin, Onyone. Col·leccions exclusives JDM, preus i on comprar.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/estilografiques" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">19</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Estilogràfiques</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Pilot Custom 74, Sailor, Platinum, laca urushi i maki-e Namiki. On comprar i preus.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/tintes" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">20</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Tintes japoneses</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Iroshizuku (24 colors), Sailor Shikiori, Kobe Ink Story. Shading, sheening i logística.
          </p>
        </a>
        <a href="/japo/papers" class="card" style="background: var(--color-bg);">
          <p class="label" style="margin-bottom: 0.75rem; color: var(--color-accent);">21</p>
          <h3 style="font-size: 1.25rem; margin-bottom: 0.5rem;">Papers japonesos</h3>
          <p style="font-size: 0.875rem; color: var(--color-muted); line-height: 1.6;">
            Tomoe River, Hobonichi Techo, MD Paper Midori, washi artesanal. On comprar i quins triar.
          </p>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

  </div>
</Layout>
